Addis Ababa
Ethiopia has arrested 15 suspected members of a terrorist group for allegedly planning attacks on the United Arab Emirates (UAE) embassy in Addis Ababa, local media Ethiopian News Agency and Ethiopian Broadcasting Corporation (EBC) reported on Wednesday.
EBC reported that the 15 suspects had taken orders from a terrorist group based in a foreign country to conduct an attack on the UAE embassy in Addis Ababa, with the objective of damaging the Ethiopian capital city's image.



